---
title: Falafel and Jeweled Couscous  with Hummus and Spicy Garlic Drizzle
description: Couscous flavoured with cumin and tumeric, then studded with almonds and cranberries, is the foundation for this tasty vegetarian meal. Crisp chickpea falafel and a duo of sauces will brighten up your day – and your tastebuds.
